# QR Code Generator

This is a simple web application that allows users to generate QR codes.

## Features

- Generate QR codes from any URL.
- Customize the color of the QR code.
- Customize the size of the QR code.
- Choose the error correction level for the QR code.
- Download the generated QR code as a PNG or SVG file.

## How to Use

1. Enter the URL that you want to generate a QR code for in the "Enter URL" input field.
2. Choose the color of the QR code by selecting a color from the color picker.
3. Enter the size of the QR code in the "QR Size" input field.
4. Choose the error correction level for the QR code from the "Error Correction Level" dropdown.
5. Click on the "Generate QR Code" button to generate the QR code.
6. The generated QR code will be displayed below the form. You can download it as a PNG or SVG file by clicking on the corresponding download link.

## Installation

1. Clone this repository: `git clone https://github.com/yourusername/qr-code-generator.git`
2. Navigate to the project directory: `cd qr-code-generator`
3. Install the dependencies: `npm install`
4. Start the server: `npm start`
5. Open your web browser and navigate to `http://localhost:3000` to use the application.

